---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Bilingual from '../../components/Bilingual.astro';
import CodeTabs from '../../components/CodeTabs.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="WebSocket · CS Notebook">
  <article class="space-y-6">
    <header>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-cyan mb-2">Networks / WebSocket</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">
        <Bilingual><span slot="zh">WebSocket</span><span slot="en">WebSocket</span></Bilingual>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh"><b>WebSocket</b> 是在单个 TCP 连接上进行<b>全双工通信</b>的协议。与 HTTP 的请求-响应模式不同，WebSocket 建立连接后，服务器可<b>主动推送</b>数据给客户端，无需客户端反复轮询。游戏场景：聊天室、实时通知、观战直播、匹配状态推送。注意：游戏内<b>高频位置同步</b>仍应使用 UDP，WebSocket 适合<b>中低频</b>的可靠实时通信。</span>
          <span slot="en"><b>WebSocket</b> enables <b>full-duplex communication</b> over a single TCP connection. Unlike HTTP's request-response model, once connected, the server can <b>push data</b> to the client without polling. Game use cases: chat rooms, real-time notifications, spectating, matchmaking status. Note: high-frequency <b>position sync</b> should still use UDP; WebSocket is for <b>medium-low frequency</b> reliable real-time communication.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">WebSocket vs HTTP 长轮询</span><span slot="en">WebSocket vs HTTP Long Polling</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">在 WebSocket 出现前，实时通信靠<b>HTTP 长轮询</b>：客户端不停发请求问"有新消息吗？"。服务器没有消息时挂起请求（hold），有消息时才响应。问题：每个请求都携带 HTTP 头（~800 字节），且每次都要重新建连（HTTP/1.1 Keep-Alive 缓解但开销仍大）。WebSocket 通过一次 <b>Upgrade 握手</b>升级为长连接，后续帧头仅 2-14 字节。</span><span slot="en">Before WebSocket, real-time communication relied on <b>HTTP long polling</b>: the client repeatedly asks "any new messages?" The server holds the request when there's nothing, responding only when data arrives. Problem: each request carries HTTP headers (~800 bytes) and may require reconnection (HTTP/1.1 Keep-Alive helps but overhead remains). WebSocket upgrades to a persistent connection via a single <b>Upgrade handshake</b>, after which frame headers are only 2-14 bytes.</span></Bilingual></p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="text-ink-muted text-left"><tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">特性</span><span slot="en">Feature</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">HTTP 轮询</span><span slot="en">HTTP Polling</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">HTTP 长轮询</span><span slot="en">Long Polling</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">WebSocket</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody class="text-ink">
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">连接模式</span><span slot="en">Connection</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">反复请求-响应</span><span slot="en">Repeated req-resp</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">请求挂起→响应</span><span slot="en">Hold→respond</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">全双工长连接</span><span slot="en">Full-duplex persistent</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">服务器推送</span><span slot="en">Server Push</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red">✗</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">被动（需先请求）</span><span slot="en">Passive</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">✓</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">单帧开销</span><span slot="en">Frame Overhead</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red">~800 字节</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red">~800 字节</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">2-14 字节</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">延迟</span><span slot="en">Latency</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">高（轮询间隔）</span><span slot="en">High</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">中</span><span slot="en">Medium</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">低（即时）</span><span slot="en">Low (instant)</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">适用场景</span><span slot="en">Use Case</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">低频查询</span><span slot="en">Low-freq query</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">中等实时</span><span slot="en">Medium real-time</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">聊天/通知/观战</span><span slot="en">Chat/notify/spectate</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">游戏位置同步</span><span slot="en">Position Sync</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red">✗</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red">✗</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">可但不推荐（用UDP）</span><span slot="en">Possible, use UDP</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">WebSocket 生命周期</span><span slot="en">WebSocket Lifecycle</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">WebSocket 连接分三个阶段：<br>
          ① <b class="text-func-amber">握手（Handshake）</b>：客户端发 HTTP GET 请求带 <code>Upgrade: websocket</code> 头，服务器返回 <b>101 Switching Protocols</b>。此后 TCP 连接升级为 WebSocket。<br>
          ② <b class="text-primary-cyan">数据帧（Data Frames）</b>：双方通过帧（Frame）收发数据。帧类型：<b>文本帧</b>（UTF-8）、<b>二进制帧</b>、<b>Ping/Pong</b>（心跳保活）、<b>Close</b>（关闭帧）。<br>
          ③ <b class="text-func-red">关闭（Close）</b>：一方发 Close 帧，另一方回 Close 帧，TCP 连接断开。</span>
          <span slot="en">WebSocket connection has three phases:<br>
          ① <b class="text-func-amber">Handshake</b>: Client sends HTTP GET with <code>Upgrade: websocket</code> header, server returns <b>101 Switching Protocols</b>. The TCP connection upgrades to WebSocket.<br>
          ② <b class="text-primary-cyan">Data Frames</b>: Both sides send/receive via frames. Frame types: <b>text</b> (UTF-8), <b>binary</b>, <b>Ping/Pong</b> (keepalive), <b>Close</b>.<br>
          ③ <b class="text-func-red">Close</b>: One side sends Close frame, the other responds with Close, TCP disconnects.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">WebSocket 帧格式</span><span slot="en">WebSocket Frame Format</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="text-ink-muted text-left"><tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">帧类型</span><span slot="en">Frame Type</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">Opcode</span><span slot="en">Opcode</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">用途</span><span slot="en">Purpose</span></Bilingual></th></tr></thead>
          <tbody class="text-ink">
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green font-mono">Continuation</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0x0</td><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">分片帧的续帧</span><span slot="en">Fragment continuation</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-primary-cyan font-mono">Text</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0x1</td><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">UTF-8 文本数据</span><span slot="en">UTF-8 text</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-primary-purple font-mono">Binary</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0x2</td><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">二进制数据</span><span slot="en">Binary data</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber font-mono">Close</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0x8</td><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">关闭连接</span><span slot="en">Close connection</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green font-mono">Ping</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0x9</td><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">心跳请求</span><span slot="en">Heartbeat request</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green font-mono">Pong</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">0xA</td><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">心跳响应</span><span slot="en">Heartbeat response</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">WebSocket 聊天室代码</span><span slot="en">WebSocket Chat Room Code</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">以下是一个游戏聊天室的完整 WebSocket 实现：服务端广播消息给所有连接的玩家，客户端处理收发。生产环境建议使用 <code>ws</code>（Node.js）或 <code>websockets</code>（Python）库。</span><span slot="en">Below is a complete WebSocket chat room implementation: the server broadcasts messages to all connected players, the client handles send/receive. In production, use <code>ws</code> (Node.js) or <code>websockets</code> (Python) libraries.</span></Bilingual></p>
      <CodeTabs
  cpp={`<pre><code>// ===== WebSocket 服务端（C++，伪代码）=====
#include &lt;unordered_set&gt;
#include &lt;websocket_server.h&gt;

// 游戏聊天室服务端
class ChatServer &#123;
    std::unordered_set&lt;WebSocketConn*&gt; clients;
    std::mutex mtx;

    void onConnect(WebSocketConn* conn) &#123;
        std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; lock(mtx);
        clients.insert(conn);
        broadcast("System", "玩家加入聊天室");
    &#125;

    void onMessage(WebSocketConn* conn, string msg) &#123;
        // 解析 JSON: &#123;"player":"Alice","text":"Hello!"&#125;
        auto data = parseJSON(msg);
        broadcast(data["player"], data["text"]);
    &#125;

    void onDisconnect(WebSocketConn* conn) &#123;
        std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; lock(mtx);
        clients.erase(conn);
        broadcast("System", "玩家离开聊天室");
    &#125;

    void broadcast(string player, string text) &#123;
        string json = R"(&#123;"player":")" + player +
                      R"(","text":")" + text + R"("&#125;)";
        for (auto* c : clients) c-&gt;send(json);  // 文本帧
    &#125;
&#125;;</code></pre>`}
  py={`<pre><code># ===== WebSocket 服务端（Python）=====
# pip install websockets
import asyncio
import json
import websockets

# 游戏聊天室服务端
clients = set()

async def handler(websocket):
    clients.add(websocket)
    try:
        await broadcast("System", "玩家加入聊天室")
        async for message in websocket:
            # 解析 JSON: {"player":"Alice","text":"Hello!"}
            data = json.loads(message)
            await broadcast(data["player"], data["text"])
    except websockets.ConnectionClosed:
        pass
    finally:
        clients.discard(websocket)
        await broadcast("System", "玩家离开聊天室")

async def broadcast(player, text):
    msg = json.dumps({"player": player, "text": text})
    # 并发发送给所有连接的客户端
    await asyncio.gather(*[c.send(msg) for c in clients])

async def main():
    async with websockets.serve(handler, "0.0.0.0", 8765):
        await asyncio.Future()  # 永久运行

asyncio.run(main())

# ===== WebSocket 客户端（浏览器 JS）=====
# const ws = new WebSocket("ws://localhost:8765");
# ws.onmessage = (e) => {
#     const data = JSON.parse(e.data);
#     console.log(data.player + ": " + data.text);
# };
# ws.send(JSON.stringify({player: "Alice", text: "Hello!"}));</code></pre>`}
      />
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">WebSocket 握手细节</span><span slot="en">WebSocket Handshake Details</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">WebSocket 握手复用 HTTP 协议完成升级：<br><br>
          <b class="text-func-amber">客户端请求：</b><br>
          <code>GET /chat HTTP/1.1</code><br>
          <code>Host: game.example.com</code><br>
          <code>Upgrade: websocket</code><br>
          <code>Connection: Upgrade</code><br>
          <code>Sec-WebSocket-Key: dGhlIHNhbXBsZSBub25jZQ==</code><br>
          <code>Sec-WebSocket-Version: 13</code><br><br>
          <b class="text-func-green">服务端响应：</b><br>
          <code>HTTP/1.1 101 Switching Protocols</code><br>
          <code>Upgrade: websocket</code><br>
          <code>Connection: Upgrade</code><br>
          <code>Sec-WebSocket-Accept: s3pPLMBiTxaQ9kYGzzhZRbK+xOo=</code><br><br>
          <code>Sec-WebSocket-Accept</code> 是服务端用 Key + 固定 GUID 做 SHA-1 再 Base64 编码，确保握手不可伪造。之后该 TCP 连接不再使用 HTTP 协议，而是 WebSocket 二进制帧协议。</span>
          <span slot="en">WebSocket handshake reuses HTTP for upgrade:<br><br>
          <b class="text-func-amber">Client request:</b><br>
          <code>GET /chat HTTP/1.1</code><br>
          <code>Host: game.example.com</code><br>
          <code>Upgrade: websocket</code><br>
          <code>Connection: Upgrade</code><br>
          <code>Sec-WebSocket-Key: dGhlIHNhbXBsZSBub25jZQ==</code><br>
          <code>Sec-WebSocket-Version: 13</code><br><br>
          <b class="text-func-green">Server response:</b><br>
          <code>HTTP/1.1 101 Switching Protocols</code><br>
          <code>Upgrade: websocket</code><br>
          <code>Connection: Upgrade</code><br>
          <code>Sec-WebSocket-Accept: s3pPLMBiTxaQ9kYGzzhZRbK+xOo=</code><br><br>
          <code>Sec-WebSocket-Accept</code> is SHA-1(Key + fixed GUID) Base64-encoded, ensuring the handshake can't be forged. After this, the TCP connection no longer uses HTTP but the WebSocket binary frame protocol.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">游戏中的 WebSocket vs UDP</span><span slot="en">WebSocket vs UDP in Games</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="text-ink-muted text-left"><tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">场景</span><span slot="en">Scenario</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">推荐</span><span slot="en">Recommended</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">原因</span><span slot="en">Reason</span></Bilingual></th></tr></thead>
          <tbody class="text-ink">
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">游戏聊天室</span><span slot="en">Game Chat</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">WebSocket</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">需可靠，中低频，浏览器原生支持</span><span slot="en">Reliable, medium-freq, browser-native</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">匹配状态推送</span><span slot="en">Match Status</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">WebSocket</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">服务器主动推送，低频</span><span slot="en">Server push, low-freq</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">观战/直播</span><span slot="en">Spectating</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">WebSocket</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">可靠数据流，浏览器兼容</span><span slot="en">Reliable stream, browser-compatible</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">实时位置同步</span><span slot="en">Position Sync</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber">UDP</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">高频、低延迟，丢包可接受</span><span slot="en">High-freq, loss-tolerant</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">射击命中判定</span><span slot="en">Hit Detection</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber">UDP</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">超低延迟，自定义可靠性</span><span slot="en">Ultra-low latency</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
